ğŸ”¸ÄÃ¢y lÃ  cÃ¡ch náº¡p (load) class Ä‘á»™ng báº±ng tÃªn (string).
"com.gpcoder.Cat" lÃ  tÃªn Ä‘áº§y Ä‘á»§ (fully qualified name) cá»§a class Cat trong package com.gpcoder.
Khi cháº¡y, JVM sáº½:
